com.android.dx.dex.file

Class DexFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.dx.dex.file.DexFile

  • public final class DexFile
extends Object
    Representation of an entire .dex (Dalvik EXecutable) file, which itself consists of a set of Dalvik classes.
